00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:36,760
I think you'd want a richer man.
College professors don't make
much money. Mark will.

306
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:43,800
I'll see that he gets over
this research business. Don't worry
about me. I'm worrying about Mark.

307
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:50,320
You needn't worry about Mark
as long as I have him, and
I've got him! The way you say that

