00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:04,640
It was very nice of you to call.

313
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:08,600
Are you coming to my party?
Do you still want me?

314
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:13,720
You have a beautiful figure. I know.
