I'm sorry, apparently you don't
think very well of me. Sure I do.

339
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:24,400
You live a very pleasant life
for a man with little charm,
less talent and no honour!

340
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:35,160
When I was a boy, Mother used to say
when I had trouble with the street
children, "Paul, regard the source."

341
00:34:35,160 --> 00:34:42,440
I'm following Mother's advice.
I came here to ask your cousin
to kindly eat her invitation,

342
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:44,480
now I think I'll use it.

